      <p>
        Hymn of the Moles is a rhythm game based on The Residents&rsquo; 1981
        album,
        <q>Mark of the Mole,</q> and its unfinished Atari game. You play as a
        <q>Mole,</q> hired to work in the mines. While working, you sing songs
        and this creates the main gameplay: hit the arrow keys in time with the
        various notes on screen and the beat.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can download the game <a href="download/moles.zip">here.</a> This is
        a Windows EXE, but I have tested it with Wine on my Linux computer and
        it works fine!
      </p>
